            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Roper科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ROP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ROP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ROP-US</a>)截至台北時間01日22:43股價上漲17.01美元，報355.40美元，漲幅5.03%，成交量179,990（股），盤中最高價355.40美元、最低價343.13美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.2%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.14%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-4.7%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Roper科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ROP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ROP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ROP-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.69%</li> <li>近 1 月：+3.95%</li> <li>近 3 月：-3.85%</li> <li>近 6 月：-24.82%</li> <li>今年以來：-23.98%</li></ul></section></main>",
